        <!-- Section Icon Component -->
        <!-- History Section -->
        <section id="history" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-icon">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square">
                    <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="18" x2="20" y2="18"/>
                    <circle cx="8" cy="6" r="2" fill="#F5F4EF"/><circle cx="16" cy="12" r="2" fill="#F5F4EF"/><circle cx="8" cy="18" r="2" fill="#F5F4EF"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div class="section-left">
                    <h2 class="section-title-zh">历史脉络</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-title-en">Historical Lineage</h3>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">追溯时间的河流，探寻马头琴的前世今生。从神话传说的朦胧起源，到世界舞台的璀璨绽放。</p>
                        <p class="en">Tracing the river of time to explore the past and present of the Morin Khuur. From the misty origins of myths and legends to its brilliant bloom on the world stage.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">马头琴的起源可追溯至唐宋时期，据《元史》和《清史稿》等史书记载，马头琴最初的装饰是龙首，后来逐渐演化成为马头的形象，是由唐宋时期的拉弦乐器奚琴逐渐演变而来。至元代，马头琴的前身"火不思"已然出现。清代时，马头琴被称为"潮尔"，是蒙古族宫廷音乐的重要乐器之一。马头琴的音色柔美深沉，极富感染力，常用于演奏蒙古族传统音乐及民间舞蹈和说唱艺术的伴奏，在蒙古族的文化中占据着举足轻重的地位。</p>
                        <p class="en">The origin of the morin khuur can be traced back to the Tang and Song dynasties. According to historical records such as the 'History of Yuan' and the 'Draft History of Qing,' the morin khuur was initially decorated with a dragon head, which gradually evolved into a horse head design. It developed from the xiqin, a bowed string instrument of the Tang and Song periods. By the Yuan dynasty, the predecessor of the morin khuur, called 'huobusi,' had already appeared. During the Qing dynasty, the morin khuur was known as 'chaor,' and it became one of the important instruments in Mongolian court music.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-right">
                    <div class="history-map">
                        <img src="assets/历史脉络图.jpg" alt="马头琴历史脉络演化图" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain;">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Culture Section -->
        <section id="culture" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-icon">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square">
                    <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="18" x2="20" y2="18"/>
                    <circle cx="4" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div class="section-left">
                    <h2 class="section-title-zh">文化与故事</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-title-en">Culture & Stories</h3>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">拨动岁月的琴弦，解码马头琴的文化基因。从草原神话的悠远回响，到跨界融合的焕新吟唱。</p>
                        <p class="en">Plucking the strings of time, decoding the cultural genes of the Morin Khuur. From the distant echoes of grassland myths to the renewed singing of cross-boundary integration.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">马头琴音乐是蒙古族草原游牧文化发展到一定历史阶段彰显其最高精神文化成就的标志性产物，它那独具特色的音色，悠扬、深沉、宽广、抒情的旋律，蕴含了独特的草原游牧审美文化、人文思想和民族精神。</p>
                        <p class="en">The music of the Morin Khuur is a hallmark of the Mongolian grassland nomadic culture reaching a certain stage of historical development and reflecting its highest achievements in spiritual and cultural expression.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bar-chart-section">
                        <h4 class="subsection-title">代表曲目</h4>
                        <p class="subsection-desc">记录了18首经典马头琴曲目名称及对应的重要性评分</p>
                        <div class="bar-chart">
                            <div class="bar" style="height:100%"><span>万马奔腾</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:90%"><span>鸿雁</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:85%"><span>苏和的白马</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:80%"><span>诺恩吉雅</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:95%"><span>达古拉</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:70%"><span>梦中的额吉</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:75%"><span>黑骏马</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:80%"><span>嘎达梅林</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:60%"><span>美丽草原我的家</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:85%"><span>回想曲</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:65%"><span>鄂尔多斯</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:75%"><span>百鸟归巢</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:50%"><span>乌兰巴托的夜</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:40%"><span>十二生肖</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:60%"><span>安代舞曲</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:70%"><span>初升的太阳</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:45%"><span>成吉思汗的两匹骏马</span></div>
                            <div class="bar" style="height:30%"><span>白音特拉</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-right center-content">
                    <div class="culture-circle">
                        <svg class="circle-svg" viewBox="0 0 600 600">
                            <defs>
                                <filter id="soft-glow">
                                    <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur"/>
