        <!-- Anatomy Section -->
        <section id="anatomy" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-icon">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square">
                    <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="18" x2="20" y2="18"/>
                    <circle cx="4" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div class="section-left">
                    <h2 class="section-title-zh">马头琴结构</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-title-en">Structure</h3>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">勾勒琴身的脉络，探寻马头琴的构造密码。从琴箱的蒙皮共鸣，到琴杆的笔直传声。</p>
                        <p class="en">Outlining the veins of the instrument's body, exploring the structural code of the Morin Khuur.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">马头琴作为蒙古族最有代表性的乐器之一，由琴体和琴弓两部分组成，并且琴体与琴弓是可以分开的。琴体是由琴头、琴杆、琴箱、琴轴、琴弦、琴码与低音梁等部分组成。</p>
                        <p class="en">The Morin Khuur, as one of the most representative instruments of the Mongolian ethnic group, is composed of two parts: the instrument body and the bow, and the body and bow can be separated.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="types-list">
                        <h4 class="subsection-title">现代马头琴种类</h4>
                        <div class="type-item"><div class="dot"></div><span class="type-name">琴身正梯形</span><div class="type-shape"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40"><polygon points="10,5 30,5 35,35 5,35"/></svg></div></div>
                        <div class="type-item"><div class="dot"></div><span class="type-name">琴身六方形</span><div class="type-shape"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40"><polygon points="20,5 35,15 35,30 20,40 5,30 5,15"/></svg></div></div>
                        <div class="type-item"><div class="dot"></div><span class="type-name">琴身八方形</span><div class="type-shape"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40"><polygon points="15,5 25,5 35,15 35,25 25,35 15,35 5,25 5,15"/></svg></div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-right">
                    <div class="anatomy-diagram">
                        <img src="assets/morin-khuur-anatomy.svg" alt="马头琴结构分解图" style="width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 600px;">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Craftsmanship Section -->
        <section id="craftsmanship" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-icon">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square">
                    <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="18" x2="20" y2="18"/>
                    <circle cx="4" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div class="section-left narrow">
                    <h2 class="section-title-zh">制作工艺</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-title-en">Craftsmanship</h3>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">描摹造琴的工序，探寻马头琴的音色密码。从琴头的图腾雕刻，到琴马的承振导音。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">作为一种传统的蒙古族乐器，马头琴以其独特的造型受到人们的广泛关注与喜爱，在 2010 年的时候，马头琴制作技艺就成为内蒙古呼和浩特市非物质文化遗产。据了解，马头琴制作技艺发展至今，大约要经过一百多道工序。</p>
                        <p class="en">As a traditional Mongolian musical instrument, the morin khuur has attracted wide attention and admiration due to its unique design. In 2010, the craft of making the morin khuur was recognized as intangible cultural heritage in Hohhot, Inner Mongolia.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="materials-section">
                        <h4 class="subsection-title">材料 <span class="en-italic">Materials</span></h4>
                        <p class="subsection-desc">马头琴的材料有五角枫、泡桐和云杉。五角枫用于马头琴的琴身制作。泡桐和云杉用于制作琴箱面板。</p>
                        <div class="material-cards">
                            <div class="material-card"><div class="material-texture maple"></div><span>五角枫</span></div>
                            <div class="material-card"><div class="material-texture paulownia"></div><span>泡桐</span></div>
                            <div class="material-card"><div class="material-texture spruce"></div><span>鱼鳞云杉</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tools-section">
                        <h4 class="subsection-title">工具 <span class="en-italic">Tools</span></h4>
                        <p class="subsection-desc">马头琴制作过程离不开不同工具的相互配合，每道制作流程使用的工具也不同。</p>
                        <div class="tool-grid">
                            <div class="tool-item">Tool</div><div class="tool-item">Tool</div><div class="tool-item">Tool</div>
                            <div class="tool-item">Tool</div><div class="tool-item">Tool</div><div class="tool-item">Tool</div>
                            <div class="tool-item">Tool</div><div class="tool-item">Tool</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-right wide">
                    <div class="craft-grid">
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 1</span></div><span class="craft-label">1. 选取板材</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 2</span></div><span class="craft-label">2. 绘制形状</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 3</span></div><span class="craft-label">3. 切割板材</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 4</span></div><span class="craft-label">4. 打磨边缘</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 5</span></div><span class="craft-label">5. 固定装饰</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 6</span></div><span class="craft-label">6. 深入雕刻马头</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 7</span></div><span class="craft-label">7. 制作调音背板</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 8</span></div><span class="craft-label">8. 固定背板</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 9</span></div><span class="craft-label">9. 背板上漆</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 10</span></div><span class="craft-label">10. 琴杆找平</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 11</span></div><span class="craft-label">11. 琴身上弦</span></div>
                        <div class="craft-card"><div class="craft-placeholder"><span>Illustration 12</span></div><span class="craft-label">12. 马头琴调音</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Heritage Section -->
        <section id="heritage" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-icon">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square">
                    <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="18" x2="20" y2="18"/>
                    <circle cx="4" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div class="section-left">
                    <h2 class="section-title-zh">传承谱系</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-title-en">Heritage Lineage</h3>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">口传心授的技法，代代相承的匠心。老一辈艺术家与年轻一代的接力，让古老音韵生生不息。</p>
                        <p class="en">Techniques passed down from master to student, craftsmanship inherited through generations. The relay between veteran artists and younger talents keeps the ancient melodies alive.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">马头琴艺术的传承谱系可追溯至近代，色拉西（1887—1968）被公认为近代马头琴艺术的奠基人。他将民间的演奏技法加以整理和规范化，培养了巴拉干、桑都仍等一批杰出弟子。其后齐·宝力高（1944— ）成为国家级代表性传承人，将马头琴推向世界舞台。2006年，蒙古族马头琴音乐被列入首批国家级非物质文化遗产名录。</p>
                        <p class="en">The lineage of Morin Khuur art can be traced back to modern times. Serashi (1887–1968) is recognized as the founder of modern Morin Khuur art. He organized and standardized folk playing techniques, training outstanding disciples such as Balagan and Sanduren. Subsequently, Qi Baoligao (1944– ) became a national-level representative inheritor, bringing the Morin Khuur to the world stage. In 2006, Mongolian Morin Khuur music was inscribed on the first National List of Intangible Cultural Heritage.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-right">
                    <div class="heritage-tree">
                        <div class="heritage-gen">
                            <span class="gen-label">第一代 · 奠基</span>
                            <div class="heritage-person founder">
                                <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C48E3C, #1E3A5F);">色</div>
                                <div class="person-info">
                                    <h4>色拉西</h4>
                                    <p>1887 — 1968</p>
                                    <span class="person-title">近代马头琴艺术奠基人</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="heritage-connector">
                            <svg width="120" height="40" viewBox="0 0 120 40"><path d="M60 0 L60 20 Q60 40 30 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M60 0 L60 20 Q60 40 90 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="heritage-gen">
                            <span class="gen-label">第二代 · 传承</span>
                            <div class="heritage-branch">
                                <div class="heritage-person">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F, #465E47);">巴</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>巴拉干</h4>
                                        <p>1916 — 1998</p>
                                        <span class="person-title">内蒙古流派代表</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="heritage-person">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #465E47, #1E3A5F);">桑</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>桑都仍</h4>
                                        <p>1924 — 2001</p>
                                        <span class="person-title">蒙古国流派代表</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="heritage-connector">
                            <svg width="180" height="40" viewBox="0 0 180 40"><path d="M90 0 L90 20 Q90 40 45 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M90 0 L90 20 Q90 40 90 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M90 0 L90 20 Q90 40 135 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="heritage-gen">
                            <span class="gen-label">第三代 · 发扬</span>
                            <div class="heritage-branch">
                                <div class="heritage-person highlight">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C48E3C, #9E4527);">齐</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>齐·宝力高</h4>
                                        <p>1944 — </p>
                                        <span class="person-title">国家级代表性传承人</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="heritage-person">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F, #C48E3C);">达</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>达日玛</h4>
                                        <p>1945 — </p>
                                        <span class="person-title">演奏家、教育家</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="heritage-person">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9E4527, #C48E3C);">布</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>布林</h4>
                                        <p>1940 — </p>
                                        <span class="person-title">西部流派大师</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="heritage-connector">
                            <svg width="240" height="40" viewBox="0 0 240 40"><path d="M120 0 L120 20 Q120 40 60 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M120 0 L120 20 Q120 40 120 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M120 0 L120 20 Q120 40 180 40" stroke="#C48E3C" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="heritage-gen">
                            <span class="gen-label">第四代 · 新生</span>
                            <div class="heritage-branch">
                                <div class="heritage-person young">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #465E47, #C48E3C);">全</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>全胜</h4>
                                        <p>1970 — </p>
                                        <span class="person-title">青年演奏家</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="heritage-person young">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C48E3C, #465E47);">陈</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>陈巴雅尔</h4>
                                        <p>1975 — </p>
                                        <span class="person-title">教育传承人</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="heritage-person young">
                                    <div class="person-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A5F, #465E47);">其</div>
                                    <div class="person-info">
                                        <h4>其日麦拉图</h4>
                                        <p>1982 — </p>
                                        <span class="person-title">新生代代表</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Performance Section -->
        <section id="performance" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-icon">
                <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6B7280" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square">
                    <line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="18" x2="20" y2="18"/>
                    <circle cx="4" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/><circle cx="4" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#6B7280"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <div class="section-left">
                    <h2 class="section-title-zh">演奏</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-title-en">Performance</h3>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">勾勒琴身的脉络，探寻马头琴的构造密码。从琴箱的蒙皮共鸣，到琴杆的笔直传声。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <div class="bilingual-block">
                        <p class="zh">马头琴是一种演奏技巧颇为复杂的乐器必须注意各部位的互相协调，用弓时右手持弓法虽与二胡相似但却有差别。由于马头琴弦是多股尼龙弦，右手要使马头琴发出纯正的乐音所需的力气要比二胡大得多，同时需要无名指和小指施加不同的压力。</p>
                        <p class="en">The morin khuur is an instrument with rather complex playing techniques, requiring careful coordination of its various parts. While the right-hand bowing technique is similar to that of the erhu, there are differences.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-right">
                    <div class="performance-grid">
                        <div class="performance-posture">
                            <span class="perf-label">Performance Posture</span>
                            <span class="perf-desc">Technical drawing of player holding the instrument.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="performance-detail">
                            <p class="zh small">演奏马头琴时，演奏者通常采取坐姿，将琴箱夹于两腿中间，琴杆偏向左侧，左手虎口稍张开，拇指微扶琴杆。在低把位上，用食指、中指的指甲顶弦，无名指按弦、小指指尖顶弦。</p>
                            <div class="hand-detail"><span>Hand Fingering Detail</span></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fingering-section">
                            <div class="fingering-chart">
                                <h4 class="fingering-title">马头琴音位、把位及指法示意图</h4>
                                <div class="fingering-placeholder"><span>Fingering Chart</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="fingering-text">
                                <div><strong>第一把位 (A调)：</strong>基础把位，最常用于低音区。<br>左弦 (A弦)：A (空弦) → B (1) → C# (2) → D (3) → E (4)<br>右弦 (D弦)：D (空弦) → E (1) → F# (2) → G (3) → A (4)</div>
                                <div><strong>第二把位 (G调)：</strong>中音区的常用把位。<br>左弦 (A弦)：G (1) → A (2) → B (3) → C (4) → D (空弦)</div>
                                <div><strong>第三把位 (D调)：</strong>高音区的转换把位。<br>左弦 (A弦)：D (1) → E (2) → F# (3) → G (4) → A (空弦)</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

